"Nadine, Desiree or Royal Blue potatoes will work well in this recipe.","Use fresh potatoes. If you clean the potatoes well, there is no need to peel them.","<strong>Vegetable potato cakes<\/strong>: replace ⅓ of the potatoes with vegetables (e.g. carrots, kohlrabi, cauliflower, zucchini etc.). Double the amount of cornflour and rolled oats. Season with ground black pepper and serve with a sour cream and herb dip.","As the batter can be prepared in seconds, it is easy to repeat this recipe quickly to increase portions for a party."],"basicInfo":["easy","45m","45m","4 portions"]}